<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- دُبُرًا لِبَهِيمَةٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- أَوْ مَيْتٍ مِمَّنْ يُجَامَعُ مِثْلُهُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- وَلَوْ نَائِمًا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٤]</span> وَإِسْلَامُ كَافِرٍ؛ وَلَوْ مُرْتَدًّا، أَوْ لَمْ يُوجَدْ مِنْه فِي كُفْرِهِ مَا يُوجِبُهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٥]</span> وَخُرُوجُ حَيْضٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٦]</span> وَخُرُوجُ دَمِ نِفَاسٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- فَلَا يَجِبُ بِوِلَادَةٍ عَرَتْ عَنْهُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٧]</span> وَمَوْتٌ تَعَبُّدًا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> غَيْرَ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#008000">(١)</span> شَهِيدِ مَعْرَكَةٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span style="color:#008000">(٢)</span> وَمَقْتُولٍ ظُلْمًا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمُصَلَّى العِيدِ لَا الجَنَائِزِ:</span> مَسْجِدٌ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- وَيَحْرُمُ تَكَسُّبٌ بِصَنْعَةٍ فِيهِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>